\fs24\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {\f1\fs20\insrsid2323119 \line }{\cs60\b\f1\fs28\insrsid2323119\charrsid2323119 Petitions}{\f1\fs28\insrsid2323119\charrsid2323119 :}{\f1\fs20\insrsid2323119 \line \line }{
\f1\insrsid2323119\charrsid2323119 
Again we pray to Thee, the Lord God, that Thou bless the good intention of Thy servants, His Eminence, the Most Reverend Metropolitan Laurus, the members of the Council of Bishops and the participants in the Pastoral Conference, and be well pleased for it
 to commence successfully, and that in due time, without any hindrance, it may reach its conclusion unto Thy glory, through the power, activity and grace of the All-Holy Spirit: We pray Thee: Hearken and have mercy!}{\f1\insrsid2323119 
\par }{\f1\insrsid2323119\charrsid2323119 That Thou assign Thy guardian angel to th
e Council of Bishops and the participants in the Pastoral Conferencer, O right solicitous Lord, and that all the hindrances of enemies, visible and invisible, may be overcome, and that Thou mayest grant success unto all who labor for a goodly conclusion, 
we pray Thee, O All-good Savior: Hearken, and have mercy!}{\f1\insrsid2323119 
\par }{\f1\insrsid2323119\charrsid2323119 Commanding, O Lord, that all things be done for Thy glory, unto Thy servants, His Eminence, the Most Reverend Metropolitan Laurus, the members of the Council of Bishops and the participants of the Pa
storal Conference, who are beginning their work for Thy glory, do Thou by Thy blessing grant a successful result and goodly conclusion, imparting to them health and length of days, we pray Thee, O most generous Creator: Hearken, and have mercy!}{
